detailedViolations.description: Background and foreground colors do not have a sufficient contrast ratio.
detailedViolations.help: Low-contrast text is difficult or impossible for many users to read. [Learn how to provide sufficient color contrast](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.9/color-contrast).

nodes.failureSummary: Fix: Background and foreground colors do not have a sufficient contrast ratio.

detailedViolations.description: Form elements do not have associated labels
detailedViolations.help: Labels ensure that form controls are announced properly by assistive technologies, like screen readers. [Learn more about form element labels](https://dequeuniversity.com/rules/axe/4.9/label).

nodes.failureSummary: Fix: Form elements do not have associated labels
